<p>The reality starlet confirmed on Friday she was no longer in contact with the former world No. 17, telling The Daily Telegraph their 'friendship is definitely over'.</p>

<p>'I do wish him the best and I hope he finds his way and surrounds himself with people who have his best interests at heart,' she added.   </p>

